OL,4,C'likely' as strike negotiations 'over'
OL,6,F"It is well known that the council has
OL,7,Fan equal pay risk, we have been
OL,8,Fnegotiating since before Christmas but
OL,9,Fhave now run out of time.
OL,11,F"We have negotiated in good faith but
OL,12,Funfortunately Unite has rejected all
OL,13,Foffers so we must now press ahead to
OL,14,Fboth address our equal pay risk and
OL,15,Fmake much needed improvements to the
OL,16,Fwaste service.
OL,18,F"This is a service that has not been
OL,19,Fgood enough for a long time and we
OL,20,Fmust improve it."
